{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_02_01_short",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 合宿を終えて (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir合宿後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the LizNoir bootcamp",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "合宿お疲れ様。一緒に行けなくてすまなかったな\n特訓をしてみてどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope the camp went well. Sorry I couldn’t be there.\nHow was all the practice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、手応えは十分です！\nライブではこれまでと違う私をお見せします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It definitely wasn’t easy‚ but I learned so much!\nI’m going to be pretty different at the next concert!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それはライブが楽しみだな。そういえば合宿中に\n愛が新しい振り付けを提案したそうじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m looking forward to that. By the way‚ I heard you\ncame up with some new choreography during the camp‚ Ai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　『The Last Chance』です\n莉央さんと相談して振り付けを変えてみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! For “The Last Chance.”\nI discussed it with Rio and made some changes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "これでファンのみなさんに\nもっと楽しんでもらえると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure the fans will really get a kick\nout of the new steps we worked in!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けを変えるのは大変だっただろ\nよく頑張ったな、愛",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s no easy feat to change the choreography.\nYou’ve been working hard‚ Ai. Well done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……ありがとうございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-thanks… for saying that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}